The North concepts Event Bus is an open source library providing event bus functioanality for your Java applications. 

See the following blogs for details:
* http://northconcepts.com/blog/2011/07/05/use-dynamic-proxies-to-create-a-simple-powerful-event-bus-part-1/
* http://northconcepts.com/blog/2011/08/12/use-dynamic-proxies-to-create-a-simple-powerful-event-bus-part-2/


This open source library is licensed under the terms of the Apache License, Version 2.0 (http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html).

Enjoy.